00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:04,600
Let Yao Zhiga investigate again.

293
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:05,640
This is against the rules.

294
00:12:05,680 --> 00:12:06,880
Look at the situation.

295
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:08,040
We need to follow the rules.

296
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,920
Why can't Sun Sheng

297
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,200
to deal with Sun Sheng?

298
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,480
Well,

299
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,560
we can't put Yao Zhiga in trouble.

300
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,520
Go to the police station

301
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,280
and say I cheated you of money.

302
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:27,360
It's about your sister's funeral.

303
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:32,520
I have an important case, Officer Yiu.

304
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:33,040
We met before.

305
00:12:33,040 --> 00:12:33,960
Does he know you?

306
00:12:34,480 --> 00:12:35,080
No, I don't remember him.

307
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:35,760
Officer Yiu.

308
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:37,880
Stop pretending. It must be for you.

309
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:38,920
Who knows you?

310
00:12:39,000 --> 00:12:39,760
Officer Yao, Yu San Xing.

311
00:12:40,800 --> 00:12:41,600
Let him in.

312
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,160
This kid.

313
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,080
Officer Yiu, I want to report a case.

314
00:12:46,760 --> 00:12:47,840
Why me?

315
00:12:48,760 --> 00:12:49,600
Because you know her.

316
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,360
It's Wu Yue. She cheated my money.

317
00:12:52,080 --> 00:12:53,160
I'm not surprised

318
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:55,960
is not surprising.

319
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,640
Tell me what happened.

320
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,120
She said

321
00:12:59,240 --> 00:13:00,680
to summon my sister's soul.

322
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:01,800
But she took my money

323
00:13:01,880 --> 00:13:02,840
but she doesn't work for me.

324
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:05,920
Hurry up and bring her back.

325
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:09,240
What's your name? Where do you live?

326
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:10,760
My name is Zhang Xiaohu.

327
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,440
I’m from Wangxi Village

328
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,520
My sister, Moth Zhang,

329
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:17,200
was killed last night.

330
00:13:17,880 --> 00:13:18,920
You said Wu Yue promised

331
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:20,640
to help your dead sister.

332
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:21,800
Yes.

333
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:23,240
Where is she now?

334
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,920
She's eating noodles at a noodle restaurant near Qin Mansion.

335
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:27,120
She used the money I gave her.

336
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:28,200
Okay.

337
00:13:29,920 --> 00:13:31,280
Let's catch Wu Yue now.

338
00:13:31,800 --> 00:13:33,560
Ask her to inform your sister.

339
00:13:37,000 --> 00:13:37,560
My lady.

340
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,120
One bowl of noodles costs three cents.

341
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:40,920
You ate a bottle of chili oil.

342
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:45,120
Please don't come here again.

343
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:48,480
I'll pay you another coin.

344
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,720
Wu Yue, where did you get the money?

345
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:00,240
Little police dog.

346
00:14:00,800 --> 00:14:01,600
You're in trouble.

347
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,600
It's her. She cheated my money.

348
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,240
How much did she cheat you?

349
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,480
This...

350
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,520
A dollar.

351
00:14:11,040 --> 00:14:12,280
Give me the money.

352
00:14:14,280 --> 00:14:16,000
It's gone. It's already spent.

353
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,040
Cut the crap.

354
00:14:17,400 --> 00:14:18,440
Give me the money.

355
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,320
or I'll take you back to the police station.

356
00:14:21,560 --> 00:14:22,560
Search if you don't believe me.

357
00:14:23,080 --> 00:14:24,800
You can find another coin on me.

358
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,840
Good for you.

359
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,320
You won't take the hard way, right?

360
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:30,760
Come with me to the police station.

361
00:14:31,400 --> 00:14:33,000
Until you pay off the money.

362
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:35,480
Is it that serious?

363
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:37,200
Wu Yue.

364
00:14:37,400 --> 00:14:38,880
Do you have any good friends

365
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:40,600
who can help you repay this silver coin?

366
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,640
For example,

367
00:14:43,440 --> 00:14:45,560
Mr. Ji?

368
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,160
No.

369
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:52,080
I fell out with my friend long ago.

370
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,400
Someone must be not loyal enough.

371
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:01,240
I don't want to make friends with him.

372
00:15:04,480 --> 00:15:04,960
Let's go.

373
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,480
Reflect on yourself in the cage in our station.

374
00:15:08,440 --> 00:15:09,680
Don't arrest her.

375
00:15:10,120 --> 00:15:11,840
If we arrest her, who will pray for my sister?

376
00:15:12,240 --> 00:15:13,680
My sister will be buried tomorrow.

377
00:15:14,120 --> 00:15:14,800
If she doesn't go,

378
00:15:15,000 --> 00:15:16,400
my sister will die in vain.

379
00:15:17,720 --> 00:15:19,160
No.

380
00:15:19,680 --> 00:15:22,120
Your sister died of injustice. She has too much resentment.

381
00:15:22,680 --> 00:15:23,360
I...

382
00:15:23,520 --> 00:15:24,480
I'm afraid of being backfired.

383
00:15:27,600 --> 00:15:29,800
It's human nature to seek advantage and avoid harm.

384
00:15:30,280 --> 00:15:31,120
Nonsense.

385
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:32,720
Isn't Chen Feng

386
00:15:32,840 --> 00:15:34,160
didn't die unjustly?

387
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:36,240
I don't think she's capable enough.

388
00:15:39,840 --> 00:15:41,720
I hate it when people question me.

389
00:15:42,040 --> 00:15:43,600
Even if I lose ten years of my life today,

390
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:44,840
I have to invite this soul.

391
00:15:45,520 --> 00:15:46,000
Xiao Hu.

392
00:15:46,360 --> 00:15:46,880
Lead the way.

393
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:47,440
Yes.

394
00:15:49,040 --> 00:15:49,520
Excuse me.

395
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:50,200
Get out of the way.
